    "# Credit Card Fraud Detection — Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "## Project 2: Leakage-Safe Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook transforms the raw fraud transaction dataset into a machine-learning-ready feature set using a **leakage-safe train/test pipeline**.\n",
    "\n",
    "The main principle is:\n",
    "\n",
    "- learn all aggregation-based features from the training data only\n",
    "- apply those learned mappings to the test data\n",
    "- fit preprocessing steps such as scaling on the training set only\n",
    "- transform the test set using the fitted training objects\n",
    "\n",
    "This ensures that the final feature dataset is realistic and valid for later modeling.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Objectives\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook will:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. load the predefined training and testing datasets  \n",
    "2. clean and standardize both datasets consistently  \n",
    "3. create time, amount, demographic, behavioral, sequential, and contextual features  \n",
    "4. learn aggregation features from the training data only  \n",
    "5. apply those learned features to the test data  \n",
    "6. encode and scale the final dataset in a leakage-safe way  \n",
    "7. export processed train and test feature files for the next project"
   ]
  },
